```plantuml
@startuml icoxfog417_karura

actor User
participant "Kintone UI" as KintoneUI
participant "Karura Client Plugin" as ClientPlugin
participant "Karura Master App" as MasterApp
participant "Karura Server" as Server
participant "Model Manager" as ModelManager
participant "Dataset" as Dataset
participant "Field Manager" as FieldManager
participant "Feature Builder" as FeatureBuilder
participant "Model Builder" as ModelBuilder

User -> KintoneUI: Interacts with Kintone app
KintoneUI -> ClientPlugin: Triggers ML action
ClientPlugin -> MasterApp: Sends configuration
MasterApp -> Server: POST /train (with config)
Server -> ModelManager: Initiate model training
ModelManager -> Dataset: Load data from Kintone
Dataset --> ModelManager: Return dataset
ModelManager -> FieldManager: Process fields
FieldManager --> ModelManager: Return processed fields
ModelManager -> FeatureBuilder: Build features
FeatureBuilder --> ModelManager: Return features
ModelManager -> ModelBuilder: Train model
ModelBuilder --> ModelManager: Return trained model
ModelManager -> Server: Save model & return status
Server --> MasterApp: Training complete
MasterApp --> ClientPlugin: Update UI status
ClientPlugin --> KintoneUI: Display results
KintoneUI --> User: Show predictions/status

@enduml
```